## A person submits their location to be shared

> backend saves session (location, user??, incentive into database)
> 
> Session has a user set timer
> 
> User can also cancel session
> 
> User can set interests/topic

```java
public class Session {
    private GeoObject location;
    private User user;
    private Incentive incentive;
    private Time time;    

    public static Session(location, user, incentive, time) {
        this.location = location;
        this.user = user;
        this.incentive = incentive;
        this.time = time;
    }
}
```
